/* Menu */
"Keeps your Mac awake while your coding agents work." = "在編碼代理程式執行時讓你的 Mac 保持喚醒。";
"On battery — plug in for long runs" = "正在使用電池——長時間執行請接通電源";
"Lid-closed needs a one-time approval" = "合蓋模式需要一次性授權";
"Always keep awake" = "始終保持喚醒";
