/* Welcome */
"I live in the menu bar and keep your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code are working — then let it sleep when they stop.\n\nThere's nothing to set up. Look for the bolt in the menu bar." = "我住在選單列裡，會在 Codex 或 Claude Code 執行時讓你的 Mac 保持喚醒，工作結束後再讓它睡眠。\n\n無需任何設定。在選單列中找閃電圖示即可。";

/* About manual */
"Keeps your Mac awake so long coding jobs finish while you're away." = "讓你的 Mac 保持喚醒，這樣即使你離開，長時間的編碼工作也能完成。";
"How it works" = "運作方式";
"It's automatic" = "全自動";
"While Codex or Claude Code are working, your Mac stays awake. When they finish, it sleeps as usual. You don't have to do anything." = "當 Codex 或 Claude Code 執行時，你的 Mac 會保持喚醒；它們結束後，Mac 會照常睡眠。你無需做任何事。";
"Turn this on to keep your Mac awake no matter what, until you turn it off." = "開啟此項可讓 Mac 始終保持喚醒，直到你將其關閉。";
"Blocks the keyboard during a run so a pet or child can't interrupt it. Press ⌘⌥⌃L to unlock." = "在工作執行時鎖定鍵盤，防止寵物或小孩打斷它。按 ⌘⌥⌃L 解鎖。";
"Keep working with the lid shut. Use it on a desk only — it pauses if your Mac gets too hot." = "合上蓋子也能繼續工作。僅限在桌面上使用——如果 Mac 過熱會自動暫停。";

