"5 minutes" = "5 分鐘";
"10 minutes" = "10 分鐘";
"15 minutes" = "15 分鐘";
"Lid closed" = "合蓋";
"Run this only with your Mac on a desk. In a bag it can't shed heat and may overheat. It pauses on its own if it gets too hot, but don't rely on that." = "僅在 Mac 放在桌面上時使用。放進包包裡會無法散熱，可能過熱。它會在過熱時自動暫停，但請不要依賴這一點。";
"Turn off lid-closed and remove its admin access." = "關閉合蓋模式並移除其管理員權限。";
"Remove" = "移除";

/* Button states */
"Allow" = "允許";
"Open Settings" = "打開設定";
"Not Set" = "未設定";

/* Lid-closed failure */
"Lid-closed mode not enabled" = "合蓋模式未啟用";
"It needs a one-time admin approval. Try again when you're ready." = "它需要一次性的管理員授權。準備好後請再試一次。";

/* Thermal back-off */
"Your Mac is getting warm, so I paused lid-closed work to protect it. It resumes automatically once it cools." = "你的 Mac 有點熱，我已暫停合蓋執行以保護它。降溫後會自動恢復。";

