"Keyboard locked" = "鍵盤已鎖定";
"Vibe Coding Guard is blocking the keyboard. Press ⌘⌥⌃L to unlock." = "Vibe Coding Guard 正在鎖定鍵盤。按 ⌘⌥⌃L 解鎖。";

